---
import "../../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>VLN and World Models - Xi Lin</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-white text-gray-900">
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16 sm:px-10">
      <a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-900">Back to home</a>
      <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">VLN and World Models</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
        My recent work focuses on embodied navigation systems, including real-robot VLN deployment, VLM-based ObjectNav, metacognitive planning for long-horizon navigation, and world-model-informed multimodal reasoning.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <img src="/assets/projects/morn-arch.png" alt="MORN system architecture" class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/projects/dual-anchor-arch.png" alt="Dual-anchoring system architecture" class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 object-cover" />
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <video controls playsinline class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-black">
          <source src="/assets/projects/morn-sim-demo.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
        <video controls playsinline class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-black">
          <source src="/assets/projects/morn-real-demo.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <section class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">JD.com Navigation Work</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
            Evaluated VLN solutions, built real-robot pipelines from data collection to deployment, and explored zero-shot VLM-based ObjectNav for transferable embodied navigation.
          </p>
        </section>
        <section class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">MORN and Dual-Anchoring</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
            Developed and contributed to systems around long-horizon navigation regulation, visual-history anchoring, and world-model-oriented reasoning for more robust embodied behavior.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
